  "notes": "## Zahlungsabgleich (Payment Auto-Matching) - FIXED v2\n\n### Audit Changes\n- FIXED: Table changed from 'invoices' to 'rechnungen' (correct schema table)\n- FIXED: Column 'total' changed to 'brutto' (correct column name in rechnungen)\n- FIXED: Status filter changed from 'sent,action_required_dunning' to 'offen' (matches rechnungen.status CHECK constraint: offen/bezahlt/storniert)\n- FIXED: Status update value changed from 'paid' to 'bezahlt' (German, matches CHECK constraint)\n- FIXED: 'paid_date' column changed to 'paid_at' (correct column in rechnungen)\n- FIXED: Removed non-existent columns: payment_transaction_id, payment_amount_received, payment_matched_by\n- FIXED: jobs_queue table replaced with automation_log (exists in schema)\n- ADDED: Error handler node for GoCardless API failures\n- NOTE: Transaction details (txn_id, amount, matched_by) now stored in automation_log.metadata JSON\n\n### Setup Required\n1. **GoCardless**: Register at bankaccountdata.gocardless.com. Obtain access token and account ID.\n2. **Env Vars**: Set GOCARDLESS_ACCESS_TOKEN and GOCARDLESS_ACCOUNT_ID in n8n\n3. **Supabase**: Set up 'Supabase API' credential in n8n\n\n### Matching Strategies (dual)\n1. **Amount match**: rechnungen.brutto within ±0.01 EUR of transaction amount\n2. **Reference match**: rechnungen.leistungsart contains transaction remittance reference\n\n### Scheduling\n- Runs at 07:00 daily (1 hour before dunning check at 08:00)\n- Processes last 7 days of transactions to catch delayed bookings"
}
